INSERT INTO `wp_comments` VALUES (1,1,'Un commentatore di WordPress','wapuu@wordpress.example','https://it.wordpress.org/','','2023-07-05 12:57:29','2023-07-05 10:57:29','Ciao, questo è un commento.\nPer iniziare a moderare, modificare ed eliminare commenti, vai alla schermata dei commenti nella bacheca.\nGli avatar di chi lascia un commento sono forniti da <a href=\"https://it.gravatar.com/\">Gravatar</a>.',0,'post-trashed','','comment',0,0),(2,83,'admin','nitin_8@yahoo.com','','::1','2016-04-02 19:06:24','2016-04-02 13:36:24','blog post sample excerpt text which can be edited by editing the blog post page. Excerpt length can be changed',0,'1','','comment',0,0),(3,202,'admin','nitin_8@yahoo.com','','::1','2016-04-05 00:45:25','2016-04-04 19:15:25','Vestibulum quam nisi, pretium a nibh sit amet, consectetur hendrerit mi. Aenean imperdiet lacus sit amet elit porta, et malesuada erat bibendum. Cras sed nunc massa. Quisque tempor dolor sit amet tellus malesuada, malesuada iaculis eros dignissim imperdiet lacus sit amet elit porta, et malesuada erat bibendum.',0,'1','','comment',0,0),(4,202,'admin','nitin_8@yahoo.com','','::1','2016-04-05 00:49:43','2016-04-04 19:19:43','Do you know a way I could add a select box for the subject field on the contact form without a lot of trouble? I’d like to give the user about 5 choices of subjects that I would hard code in. I’m using the html template theme.',0,'1','','comment',3,0),(5,552,'Cobus Bester','bester.c@gmail.com','','196.215.9.147','2013-06-07 11:57:05','2013-06-07 11:57:05','Simple and effective design. One of my favorites.',0,'1','','review',0,0),(6,553,'Cobus Bester','bester.c@gmail.com','','196.215.9.147','2013-06-07 11:53:49','2013-06-07 11:53:49','Wonderful quality, and an awesome design. WooThemes ftw!',0,'1','','review',0,0),(7,553,'Andrew','andrew@chromeorange.co.uk','','86.19.152.140','2013-06-07 11:57:45','2013-06-07 11:57:45','This t-shirt is awesome! Would recommend to everyone!\n\nI\'m ordering mine next week